---
title: Seared Steak & Caramelised Onion Subs with Golden Fries & Basil Pesto
description: Love a good steak sambo? Meet our latest "don't go out when you can make it (better!) at home" recipe. Little touches like oven-baked ciabatta, caramelised onion and basil pesto are what take it from good to great.
